code: "use strict";export function checkDuplicateRouteNames(state){const duplicates=[];const getRouteNames=(location,state)=>{state.routes.forEach(route=>{const currentLocation=location?`${location} > ${route.name}`:route.name;route.state?.routeNames?.forEach(routeName=>{if(routeName===route.name){duplicates.push([currentLocation,`${currentLocation} > ${route.name}`]);}});if(route.state){getRouteNames(currentLocation,route.state);}});};getRouteNames('',state);return duplicates;}
